data.msg: Hi Stace
The past year,
I made you this mixtape
I added to it whenever I heard a song that reminded me of you
I love you !!
very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very very much !!
It's been an eventful year
With it's ups and downs
Thank you for being mine. It's been such a pleasure to love you & grow our love together.
Putting this together,
I tried to collage all the images of what we shared,
to create a time capsule of our year
I'm so grateful for every moment
And for you coming into my life
You're the most wonderful dance partner
Happy Anniversary, my love
Anyways, I'll do my best to provide some context on this listening journey
I hope you like it
This song is 'Really Love' by D'Angelo. I heard it a few weeks ago again.
And it just filled my heart with feelings of you
This next song is 'Oração' by Agnes Nunes
It means 'Prayer' in Portuguese, I think it sounds so beautiful
Here's some of the lyrics
'I met you going the wrong way, I melted'
'Oh my dear, what a sweet fantasy, you here'
'A sailboat, the two of us, a blanket'
'All I ask for in this life'
'Don't hurt this poor heart'
'It's all I imagined, smiling'
'I will make this my prayer'
'Dear love, everything will be alright'
'Whoever sees you, wants to have you close'
ଘ(੭*ˊᵕˋ)੭* ̀ˋ
This next song is 'Intimate' by Erika de Casier
It reminds me of us ;)
I love getting up 2 no good with you ;)
This is 'No Sleeep' by Janet Jackson
I fucking love this song
And it really reminds me of the sleepless nights
When we can't keep our hands off each other
This next song is 'Don't Be So Hard on Your Own Beauty (MY HEART REMIX) by yeule
I've always loved this song, and it's always meant a lot to me. It means even more now, having shared it with you
It reminds me of how we show up for, and see, each other
Including it here though, as it was, just didn't feel special enough !
So I made this remix
I hope you like it !
(This is my favorite part of the mixtape)
Thank you again for sharing your life with me
I love you
ღゝ◡╹ )ノ♡
okie so what'd you think ?? lmk
Anyways, this next song is 'Uh-Huh' by Tinashe
This is the first song I saved on the playlist
She had just put out a new EP when we started dating
And this song was pretty sexy, and reminded me of you
This next song is 'Soñar' by Belanova
I think its rly pretty & sweet
I can't wait to go dancing with you soon
This next song is 'Gold Splatter' by Black Moth Super Rainbow
I was never too into them when I was younger
Rediscovering them, I see how beautiful their music is
And this song sounds like a beautiful day with you
It was cool you knew them, I hope you like this song too
I can picture us on adventures, when I hear this
Things are just more fun with you
This next song is 'Be a Toy' by Title Fight
Title Fight was my favorite band when I was 20 years old lol
I lowkey wanted to drop out of school just to join a band and be like Title Fight
But I didn't play any instruments so that would've been a bad idea
Anyway over the years, this song started to sound kinda sexy lmfao
I like when we get to be each other's toy hehe
********* beee a toyyy foreverrrrrr *********
This next song is 'Sugar' by BROCKHAMPTON
It's such a sweet song
'You're the only one I want by my side, when I fall asleep'
'I know it's hard, but we need each other
~ I WAAAANTTT YOUUUUU II WANT YOUUUUUU ~
This next song is 'King of Silence' by Cibo Matto
I told you about it, and I debated putting it in
It's kinda bittersweet ...
But when I hear it, it moves me so much and reminds me of us
You show me so much love & patience & compassion
Thank you for letting me rest my head on you
I've never really felt able to do that
I feel this song also reflects how it feels like you just *see* me
The way you love inspires me to love you with all my heart
Ok, this is it
The last song ...
It's 'Je t'aime moi non plus' by Serge Gainsbourg & Jane Birkin
It's a sexy, lustful song, that I heard in a movie on the flight home from Europe
(i didn't know it was a lil fucked up tho, i just thought it was sexy & a little funny lol)
It reminds me of being in our Paris apartment, getting crepes late at night
Thank you for such a wonderful year, my love. I look forward to so many more
I hope this was cool & fun & you liked it
Happy Anniversary <3
The End
